      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Just a few fixes and performances improvement :\r\n* Layout is now updated on resize (thanks to @brendon-felix-hp), and after cards width have been updated, removing some of the weird display bugs that could happen on mobile\r\n*  Only the first hundred characters of each note are rendered, improving rendering performance. Cards have a fixed max height, improving display of elements such as tables.",
