      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "* Add support for most of Obsidian official search plugin [syntax](https://help.obsidian.md/Plugins/Search#Search+terms). You can now do complex queries such as `lorem OR (ipsum -tag:#Tag1)`. The only difference from official search plugin syntax are `block:`, `section:` and `task*:` operators, which are not implemented.\r\n* Add a *Base query* setting which allow to configure which notes are displayed in Card view when you open it. With a `-(negative query)`, this can be used to exclude a folder, exclude a particular tag, or simply hide notes matching a particular keyword. ",
